General.Name: YoungQin International Co
General.Description: YoungQin International Co., Ltd. operates a franchise of chain restaurants in Taiwan and internationally. The company also offers fried chicken products under the Fried Chicken Master brand name. It also engages in the catering and bread baking operations. The company was founded in 2015 and is based in Taoyuan City, Taiwan.
General.Address: No. 16, Hejiang Road, Taoyuan City, Taiwan, 320
